    <body>
        <section name="Building from sources">
            <p>
                Check out the <a href="/cvs.html">CVS repository</a> and build
                it with <a href="http://maven.apache.org/">Maven</a>.
            </p>
            <p>
                Useful goals:
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        build distribution: <code>maven aspectwerkz:jar</code> (or
                        <code>ant dist</code> if you prefer Ant)
                    </li><br/>
                    <li>
                        run the tests: <code>maven aspectwerkz:test</code>
                    </li><br/>
                    <li>
                        run examples: <code>maven aspectwerkz:samples:&lt;name_of_example&gt;</code>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <p>
                You can also download the distribution from the
                <a href="/releases.html">Releases</a> page.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section name="Install">
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Make shure that <code>JAVA_HOME</code> is set.
                    </li><br/>
                    <li>
                        Set the <code>ASPECTWERKZ_HOME</code> variable to point
                        to the root of the distribution.
                    </li><br/>
                    <li>
                        Add <code>ASPECTWERKZ_HOME/bin</code> to your path.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </section>

    </body>

</document>

